            <thetext>The TextField should add a &quot;readOnly&quot; state via the _applyReadOnly property applyier:

    _applyReadOnly : function(value, old)
    {
      if (this._inputElement) {
        this._inputElement.readOnly = value;
      }

      if (value) {
        this.addState(&quot;readOnly&quot;);
      } else {
        this.removeState(&quot;readOnly&quot;);
      }
    }

This would allow to visually reflect the readOnly state via appearance.</thetext>
